<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Closes the game page layout and renders the sidebar.

Place this at the end of game page content, after all wiki text.

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Game
| Name = Example Game
| Deck = Short description...
| Platforms = Platforms/PC, Platforms/PlayStation
...
}}

== Overview ==
Wiki content here...

== Gameplay ==
More content...

{{GameEnd}}
</pre>

===Structure===
This template closes the following divs opened by <code><nowiki>{{Game}}</nowiki></code>:
* <code>.gb-game-wiki-content</code>
* <code>.gb-game-main</code>

Then renders the Similar Games card grid (ranked via the GBRelated store) and
the sidebar via <code><nowiki>{{GameSidebar}}</nowiki></code>, and closes:
* <code>.gb-game-content</code>
* <code>.gb-game-page</code>
</noinclude><includeonly></div>
<div id="SimilarGames" class="gb-games-section" style="clear:both">
<div class="gb-games-section-header"><h2 class="gb-games-section-title">Similar Games</h2></div>
{{#invoke:Related|cards|similar|limit=12}}
</div>
</div><div class="gb-game-sidebar">{{GameSidebar}}</div></div></div></includeonly>
